{"tid":528185,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"NVIDIA 更新 GPU 驅動以防 CPU 受到 Spectre 漏洞影響","createTime":"2018-01-13T13:32:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-15T05:51:13.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"201d649376cc05364240ee9122c3eadc5bf6e39b","tid":528185,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T13:32:54.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://chinese.engadget.com/2018/01/11/nvidia-gpu-cpu-spectre/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchinese.engadget.com%2F2018%2F01%2F11%2Fnvidia-gpu-cpu-spectre%2F&d=O%2BsyYLFTxwcZnUDajpZneQHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=a550c993\" target=\"_blank\">https://chinese.engadget.com/2018/01/11/nvidia-gpu-cpu-spectre/</a><br />\n<br />\n對於讓人很頭痛的 Meltdown、Spectre 漏洞，其實不單單只是處理器或作業系統廠家需要出patch而已啊。今天早些時候 NVIDIA 宣布會為旗下多款產品更新驅動程式，以防止其搭配的 CPU 受到漏洞的影響。據了解，所有 GeForce、Quadro、NVS、Tesla 和 GRID 芯片都都在更新之列，GPU 本身不存在問題，主要是原來的程式碼可能會讓對應的處理器至少面臨 Spectre（variant 1）漏洞的風險。Spectre（variant 2）的狀態是「可能影響」，Meltdown（variant 3）倒是不用操心。目前 NVIDIA 那邊已經針對第一類情況推出了安全更新（除了 Tesla 和 GRID 要等到一月末，其它產品的更新大部分已上線），並且承諾接下來也會著手解決第二類的隱患。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/midas/888ec7c422ac9e9181e8d7a51befadd4/206018360/gtx-1080-review-gallery-12-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.aolcdn.com%2Fhss%2Fstorage%2Fmidas%2F888ec7c422ac9e9181e8d7a51befadd4%2F206018360%2Fgtx-1080-review-gallery-12-1.jpg&h=72bd657d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>不過，NVIDIA 目前還沒有透露更新會不會拖累到效能...</strong></span></div>"},{"pid":"a376060ce05022caa8d09a1ecaf2abb6e381cf41","tid":528185,"uid":151490,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T02:24:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"02cb958e3569fa4a5a46360a7b1798f17d575509","tid":528185,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a376060ce05022caa8d09a1ecaf2abb6e381cf41","tid":528185,"uid":151490,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,